response.original_title: I Know What You Did Last Summer
response.overview: After an accident on a winding road, four teens make the fatal mistake of dumping their victim's body into the sea. Exactly one year later, the deadly secret resurfaces as they're stalked by a hook-handed figure.
response.tagline: If you're going to bury the truth, make sure it stays buried.
